N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1ยง 1.8 - Results of tests to be reported

State Regulations

The operator of each approved laboratory shall promptly
report to the commissioner and to the processor the result of each test made on
each sample submitted as provided in section
1.7
of this Part. Notes
